quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  40,28,"waqal rajul muwmin biallah min al frewn, yaktum 'iimanah mnkrana ealaa qwmh: kayf tsthlwn qatl rajul la jaram lah eindakum 'iilaa 'an yaqul rabiy allh, waqad ja'akum balbrahyn alqatet min rabikum ealaa sidq ma yqwl? fa'iina yak musaa kadhbana f'inn wbal kadhibuh eayid ealayh whdh, wa'iin yak sadqana lhqkm baed aladhi ytweeadkm bh, 'iina allah la yuafiq lalhaqu man hu mtjawz llhd, bitark alhaqu wal'iqbal ealaa albatl, kdhdhab bnsbth ma 'asraf fih 'iilaa allh"
  40,29,"ya qawm lakum alsultan alyawm zahirin fi 'ard \"msr \" ealaa reytkm min bani 'iisrayiyl wghyrhm, fman yadfae eanaa eadhab allah 'iin hll bna? qal fireawn liqawmih mjybana: ma arykm- 'ayuha alnas- min alraay walnsyht 'iilaa ma 'araa linafsi walakum slahana wswabana, wama 'adeukum 'iilaa 'iilaa tariq alhaqu walswab"
  40,30,"wqal alrajul almumin min al fireawn lifireawn wamalayih waezana wmhdhrana: 'iiniy 'akhaf ealaykum 'iin qutiltum mwsa, mithl yawm al'ahzab aladhin thzzabu ealaa anbyayhm"
  40,31,"mthl eadatan qawm nuh waead wathamud wman ja' baedihim fi alkufr waltkdhyb, ahlkhm allah bsbb dhalik. wama allah subhanah yurid zlmana llebad, fayueadhibuhum bighayr dhanb adhnbwh. taealaa allah ean alzulm walnqs elwana kbyrana"
  40,32,"wya qawm 'iiniy 'akhaf ealaykum eiqab yawm alqyamt, yawm yunadi fih bed alnaas bedana; min hwl almawqif dhlk alywm"
  40,33,"ywm tualuwn dhahbyn harbyn, ma lakum min allah min mane yamnaekum wanasir ynsrkm. wman ykhdhlh allah walam ywfqh 'iilaa rshdh, fama lah min had yahdih 'iilaa alhaqi walswab"
  40,34,"walaqad 'ursil allah 'iilaykum alnby alkarim yusif bin yaequb ealayhima alsalam min qibal mwsa, baldlayl alwadihat ealaa sdqh, wamrkm bieibadat allah wahdah la sharik lh, fama ziltum mrtabyn mimaa ja'akum bih fi hyath, hataa 'iidha maat aizdad shkkm wshrkkm, wqltm: 'iina allah ln yursil min baedih rswla, mithl dhlk aldalal yudill allah kl mtjawz llhq, shakk fi whdanyt allah teala, fala ywfqh 'iilaa alhudaa walrshad"
  40,35,"aldhyn ykhasmwn fi ayat allah whjjh ldfeha min ghyr 'an yakun ladayhim hujat mqbwlt, kabur dhlk aljidal mqtana eind allah waeind aladhin amnu, kama khatam baldlal whajab ean alhudaa qulub hwla' almkhasmyn, yakhtim allah ealaa qalb kl mstkbr ean tawhid allah wtaeth, jabaar bikathrat zulmih wedwanh"
  40,36,"wqal fireawn mkdhdhibana lmwsa fi dewth 'iilaa al'iqrar birabi alealamin waltslym lh: ya haman abn li bnana' ezymana; laealiy 'ablugh 'abwab alsamawat wama ywslny 'ilyha, fanzr 'iilaa 'ilh musaa bnfsy, wa'iiniy lazn musaa kadhbana fi dewah 'ana lana rbana, wa'anah fawq alsmawat, whkdha zuyan lifireawn eamalih alsyiy farah hsnana, wsudd ean sabil alhq; bsbb albatil aldhy zuyin lh, wama aihtial fireawn wtdbyrh l'iyham alnaas 'anah mhq, wamusaa mbtl 'illa fi khsar wbwar, la yfydh 'iilaa alshqa' fi aldunya walakhrt"
  40,37,"wqal fireawn mkdhdhibana lmwsa fi dewth 'iilaa al'iqrar birabi alealamin waltslym lh: ya haman abn li bnana' ezymana; laealiy 'ablugh 'abwab alsamawat wama ywslny 'ilyha, fanzr 'iilaa 'ilh musaa bnfsy, wa'iiniy lazn musaa kadhbana fi dewah 'ana lana rbana, wa'anah fawq alsmawat, whkdha zuyan lifireawn eamalih alsyiy farah hsnana, wsudd ean sabil alhq; bsbb albatil aldhy zuyin lh, wama aihtial fireawn wtdbyrh l'iyham alnaas 'anah mhq, wamusaa mbtl 'illa fi khsar wbwar, la yfydh 'iilaa alshqa' fi aldunya walakhrt"